(a+1)^3-a^3 = m^2 \Rightarrow 3a^2+3a+1=m^2\Rightarrow 9a^2+9a+3=3m^2\Rightarrow (3a+1)^2+3a+2=3m^2
t^2+t+1-3m^2 = 0 \rightarrow t = \dfrac{-1\pm\sqrt{1-4(1-3m^2)}}2\Rightarrow t=\dfrac{-1\pm\sqrt{12m^2-3}}2
t=\dfrac{\sqrt{12m^2-3}-1}2
\sqrt{12m^2-3} = k \Rightarrow k^2 = 3(4m^2-1)
